{"tid":1130780,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兒子嬉戲遭抓傷 澳門躁父一拳打死七旬翁","createTime":"2019-04-29T09:24:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T01:01:58.000Z","uid":130626,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"08959964d8e1366a87a836ae2372c7307a33d623","tid":1130780,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T09:24:56.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】澳門發生命案，一名36歲地產經紀疑因不滿兒子被另一男童抓傷，揮拳打傷對方的74歲外祖父，男童外祖父最終傷重不治。<br />\n澳門司警表示，疑犯陪同5歲兒子到下環街市內的休憩區玩耍，兒子期間被1名9歲男童抓傷，疑犯要與男童父母理論，男童將疑犯帶返住所，同住的外祖父拒絕賠償並表示要報警。有人揮動右拳擊中男童外祖父左面面頰，男童外祖父送院後證實腦出血及腦水腫，延至昨日早上不治。<br />\n司警稱，疑犯承認一時氣憤犯罪，由於動機微不足道，涉嫌觸犯「嚴重傷害他人身體完整性」及「因結果之加重」，將他移交檢察院。若罪名成立，最高可被判監20年。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%85%92%E5%AD%90%E5%AC%89%E6%88%B2%E9%81%AD%E6%8A%93%E5%82%B7-%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80%E8%BA%81%E7%88%B6-%E6%8B%B3%E6%89%93%E6%AD%BB%E4%B8%83%E6%97%AC%E7%BF%81-081800382.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%2585%2592%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%25AC%2589%25E6%2588%25B2%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%258A%2593%25E5%2582%25B7-%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E9%2596%2580%25E8%25BA%2581%25E7%2588%25B6-%25E6%258B%25B3%25E6%2589%2593%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E4%25B8%2583%25E6%2597%25AC%25E7%25BF%2581-081800382.html&d=5ezJA%2FdytRM7iHrFGdkn9btFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=bec8a44c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%85%92%E5%AD%90%E5%AC%89%E6%88%B2%E9%81%AD%E6%8A%93%E5%82%B7-%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80%E8%BA%81%E7%88%B6-%E6%8B%B3%E6%89%93%E6%AD%BB%E4%B8%83%E6%97%AC%E7%BF%81-081800382.html</a>"},{"pid":"ced509a038ee5b4b7d15daf825352d31a53ce59e","tid":1130780,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T19:28:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"92fc94afe5956f30c3d8a2f158a2583d94257d7c","tid":1130780,"uid":22974,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T19:37:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6cd07535036384f9b1a9fac5825c3395f0b2d356","tid":1130780,"uid":136662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T19:38